    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in stunning, showroom-ready shape\u2014honestly, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the lot yesterday! It\u2019s been totally pampered since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and it still drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019ve been looking for that perfect, 'like-new' ride without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
