    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a pristine example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six remains factory-spec, delivering instantaneous throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen features a bulletproofed VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the chassis's known stress points. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal lateral traction. With zero bushing deflection and an immaculate undercarriage, this vehicle offers the precise mechanical feedback of a showroom-fresh unit. A turn-key investment for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
