    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment since its original delivery. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero imperfections, chips, or swirl marks, complemented by pristine alloy wheels wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear or creasing, and it still carries that distinctive new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced navigation, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented exclusively at authorized dealerships. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
